ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would recommend this course because of course we must learn psychotherapy technique before we actually use it!
I would recommend this course. It was an important foundation to the beginning of our clinical training and provided us with a survey of current, relevant techniques that were empirically supported.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: It was an introduction to psychotherapy technique, and the final assignment especially was helpful in preparing me to actually handle a case.

This course influenced how I viewed clinical interactions and the importance of the clinician-client interaction. I believe that the continued clinical training will influence how I conceptualized my own research through its emphasis on psychiatric disorders and how they are addressed clinically.
